CQL_CHAR:
library NUMBER version '1'
parameter VALUE default 10
context Unfiltered
define NUMBER: VALUE > 0

library TEXT version '1'
parameter VALUE default 'abc'
context Unfiltered
define TEXT: Length(VALUE) > 0

library DATE version '1'
parameter VALUE default '2022-01-02'
context Unfiltered
define STRING: Length(VALUE) > 0
define SPLIT: Length(Split(VALUE, '-')) = 3
define SPLIT_1: Length(Split(VALUE, '-')[0]) = 4
define SPLIT_2: Length(Split(VALUE, '-')[1]) = 2
define SPLIT_3: Length(Split(VALUE, '-')[2]) = 2

library BLOB version '1'
parameter VALUE default 'abc'
context Unfiltered
define TEXT: Length(VALUE) > 0
